author: dolander
msg: In this change the <netui:label> was renamed to <netui:span>.  This was an
issue in the 8.1 tags because <netui:label> does not output the HTML <label> using in 508 complience inside forms.
Because the netui tags are HTML specific, we decided to rename label to span because <span> is
the HTML output by the label tag.  The next checkin will rename the <netui:formLabel> to <netui:label>.
svn doesn't allow this type of rename in a single change.
The bulk of this change is updating the tag usage in the tests.
